{"tid":1418623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我對唔住前線手足！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:42:50.000Z","uid":195930,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cc06d9844d6d102894fcd81d1fe40de057a6a20e","tid":1418623,"uid":195930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:05.000Z","msg":"今晚我依條衰仔讚左前線貪戀權力個post<br />\n我諗左一陣就發現<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我錯了</span><br />\n<br />\n係一個極度緊張既情況下，草木皆兵係一件無可厚非既事。你永遠唔知幾時，咩人，咩目的黎影你相。光復行動去到今日，全香港人都知道前線係要背負幾高風險。<br />\n而且香港人鍾意打卡已經去到病態，好多街坊行過睇到咁大場面都忍唔住會影相。<br />\n所以各位前線每次見到，求你地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將不滿表達出黎！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持你的人，永遠不會離棄你</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最簡單解決方法，就係一啖砂糖一啖屎！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有手足鬧完人，其他有體貌既前線，市民，和理非幫手解釋，好似警犬記你老母後，狗大佬都幫佢地講說話，我地和理非唔洗驚前線鬧走同路人，唔好指責，不如諗下點幫佢地解決途人影相，幫佢地同街坊say個sorry，教識街坊！</span>"},{"pid":"9e83fd844ecba944df711649aa5db93536f4f2f3","tid":1418623,"uid":195930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"634ff6e31fbd8e8662043a8e437659e9ff9b708a","tid":1418623,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:31.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割!"},{"pid":"30c535f7c5fd8a3a6b4c32f321ede79b4bfaf6e1","tid":1418623,"uid":195930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fecd116a9cf784d2912be9356316bb0f439c4e70","tid":1418623,"uid":195930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:45.000Z","msg":"對唔住前線"},{"pid":"2e0b53afddfcd3e4cf780e957d9ff75a52c4317c","tid":1418623,"uid":195930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:58.000Z","msg":"我知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab0bc3fa72b05d56f251cfbae4f4170884c5dda","tid":1418623,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited